casebody.data:
K.R.
v.
S.C. (People). No. S231709. Supreme Court of California March 9, 2016. CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, and CUÉLLAR, JJ., concur.

The petition for review is granted. The request for stay is denied. The stay previously issued by the Court of Appeal is dissolved.

KRUGER, J., was absent and did not participate.
